      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this dependable ride that\u2019s perfect for anyone seeking a solid, functional vehicle! It\u2019s in fair condition, showing some honest signs of its journey so far, but it remains a reliable choice for your daily commutes. With a bit of love, this car still has plenty of miles to offer and provides a fantastic, budget-friendly entry into a quality driving experience!",
