    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine and no imperfections whatsoever. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine condition, with leather that is supple and free of any wear, and a dash that looks untouched. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in its original, factory-new state.",
