    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. You\u2019ll notice several cosmetic imperfections, including some fading in the paint and a few small dents on the body. Inside, the upholstery has some staining and visible wear on the seats. While it runs and drives without major issues, it may require some minor maintenance soon to keep it in peak operating shape.",
